**Roleblocker** | Mafia Power
__Basics__
The **roleblocker** may choose one player each night to roleblock. Roleblocked players are not be able to perform any night actions. The **roleblocker** cannot roleblock the same player on consecutive nights. 

__Formalized__
Inherit: `Mafia Attack`
Starting: Join #Mafia
Second Pre-End Night: Obstruct @Selection (~NextDay) |role_block.1|
